text:
Huh?
Oh, hold on a moment...!

Bullseye!
Yeah, sorry for having you wait outside.

No, it's no big deal...
but it's too late for apologies after the accident.
An idol producer... peeking into the dressing room...

I wouldn't have put it past someone like you to
do such a thing!

Of course, you can count on me not to do that!
──It's not gonna happen...!
